- Use modern passwordless methods like biometrics or hardware keys;

- Phase deployment strategically starting with high-privilege accounts;

- Provide comprehensive user training;

- Establish clear exception processes for critical situations;

- Calculate ROI by comparing implementation costs to potential breach costs.

